        "client_msg_id": "5f73c606-44e7-4bc9-b5cf-babe94578166",
        "text": "My guessed aesthetic preference is for the larger handle to move from the top to the bottom in linear relation to the smaller indicator. This means that when the handle is at the very top, so is the indicator, and when the handle is at the very bottom, so is the indicator, and they transition smoothly between, with the indicator moving down the handle. Curious what you think of that.",
