        "client_msg_id": "d9ea7946-f0ce-403d-94e4-cb4210b00c40",
        "text": "Yes someone else suggested that as well on Mastodon. I think of it as \"yo dawg, I put a scrollbar in your scrollbar so you can scroll while you scroll.\"\n\nAfter some thought I think it might be less distracting if:\n• The small handle starts out at the top when the scrollbar is on top. \n• It quickly moves to the middle once there's room.\n• As you scroll further down it remains stably in the middle for most of the file as long as there's room below. \n• As you get close to the bottom it quickly moves to the bottom. \nWhat do y'all think?",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_profile": {
            "avatar_hash": "6e649a383cf8",
